{"tid":1060913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美好白人家園]  被控策劃國內恐怖襲擊的美國海岸警衛隊員否認指控","createTime":"2019-03-14T04:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T05:02:53.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1b7227d4a7ff88db55a2cc8bd915576d1a9274c9","tid":1060913,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T04:46:48.000Z","msg":"被控策劃國內恐怖襲擊的美國海岸警衛隊員否認指控<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-coast-guard-terror/4827091.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fus-coast-guard-terror%2F4827091.html&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=a093e845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-coast-guard-terror/4827091.html</a><br />\n<br />\n被控策劃國內恐怖襲擊的美國海岸警衛隊員目前仍在監獄等待審判，此前他否認了有關武器和毒品的指控。克里斯托弗&middot;哈森中尉星期一在馬里蘭州的一個聯邦地區法院否認了對他的指控。上個月他被捕後，警方在他位於華盛頓郊區的公寓裡發現了十幾件武器和數千發子彈。據稱在他的住所還發現了非法毒品。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">檢察官表示，哈森想要建立一個&ldquo;白人家園&rdquo;，並列出了一份暗殺自由主義政治人物的名單。</span></span>如果所有罪名成立，哈森可能被判30年以上監禁。"},{"pid":"58cabbfc34d9c1459b8fe00409a3fc42a166fd18","tid":1060913,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:02:53.000Z","msg":"rainbow 6 patriots<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}